00:29:48,369 --> 00:29:50,872
Tomorrow will be my plea hearing.

528
00:29:51,414 --> 00:29:55,752
I will plead guilty so my
sentence will be shorter.

529
00:29:56,461 --> 00:29:57,253
Dad.

530
00:30:00,298 --> 00:30:01,758
I remember it now.

531
00:30:05,512 --> 00:30:08,389
You didn’t kill Zach.

532
00:30:11,434 --> 00:30:12,310
It was me.

533
00:30:16,564 --> 00:30:18,274
I poisoned him.

534
00:30:24,572 --> 00:30:26,074
Liv, come here!

535
00:30:31,287 --> 00:30:32,496
I was calling you.

536
00:30:32,497 --> 00:30:33,748
You didn't hear me?

537
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:35,875
Let go of me.

538
00:30:36,209 --> 00:30:37,544
Why won’t you give it to me?

539
00:30:37,877 --> 00:30:39,211
You’re such a pig.

540
00:30:39,212 --> 00:30:40,463
Go to your mistress!

541
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:43,715
I want you!

542
00:30:43,716 --> 00:30:44,759
- What's wrong?
- Let me go!

543
00:30:45,176 --> 00:30:46,845
Let me go!

544
00:30:49,514 --> 00:30:50,932
- You want it the hard way, huh?
- Stop it!

545
00:30:51,558 --> 00:30:52,350
- Get inside!
- [LIV WHIMPERS]

546
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:53,685
[LIV GROANS]

547
00:30:54,185 --> 00:30:55,103
- [LIV GRUNTS]
- [ZACH GROANS]

548
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:55,937
[ZACH GROANS]

549
00:30:56,771 --> 00:30:57,605
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]

550
00:30:57,939 --> 00:30:59,440
[ZACH GRUNTS]

551
00:30:59,816 --> 00:31:01,234
Open the door!

552
00:31:01,442 --> 00:31:03,569
[LIV PANICALLY BREATHING]

553
00:31:03,570 --> 00:31:04,571
Open the door, Liv!

554
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,406
Open the door, Liv!

555
00:31:07,407 --> 00:31:08,741
I’m telling you!

556
00:31:10,785 --> 00:31:12,704
[ZACH BREATHES HEAVILY]

557
00:31:13,121 --> 00:31:16,583
[LIV PANICALLY BREATHING]

558
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,543
[LIV INHALES SHARPLY] No.

559
00:31:32,724 --> 00:31:34,474
[LIV PANICALLY BREATHING]

560
00:31:34,475 --> 00:31:36,603
No, no, no, no, no, no!

561
00:31:42,025 --> 00:31:44,152
[LIV SOBBING]

562
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:46,195
[CAR BEEPS]

563
00:31:46,446 --> 00:31:47,989
- [CAR DOOR OPENS]
- [LIV PANICALLY BREATHING]

564
00:31:49,407 --> 00:31:51,284
- [ZACH GRUNTS]
- [LIV PANICALLY BREATHING]

565
00:31:51,618 --> 00:31:53,786
No, no, no!

566
00:31:54,704 --> 00:31:56,331
[LIV SOBBING]

567
00:31:56,706 --> 00:31:59,417
[LIV CRYING] No! No!

568
00:31:59,709 --> 00:32:01,711
[LIV CRIES]

569
00:32:02,545 --> 00:32:05,048
[LIV CRYING] No!

570
00:32:18,061 --> 00:32:19,604
Baby, I’m sorry.

571
00:32:21,230 --> 00:32:24,567
Baby, I’m sorry, okay?
It will only hurt the first time.

572
00:32:30,448 --> 00:32:33,242
When you get home, just take a shower.
It will feel better.

573
00:32:34,243 --> 00:32:35,745
Baby, I’m sorry, that’s not me.

574
00:32:36,245 --> 00:32:37,245
[WHISPERS] You have to believe me.

575
00:32:37,246 --> 00:32:38,664
That’s not me.

576
00:32:38,665 --> 00:32:39,916
I’m sorry.

577
00:32:40,833 --> 00:32:41,459
I’m sorry.

578
00:32:42,126 --> 00:32:43,044
I'm sorry, Liv.

579
00:32:49,717 --> 00:32:51,511
Liv, come on!

580
00:33:00,144 --> 00:33:01,354
Don’t touch me.

581
00:33:08,778 --> 00:33:09,903
Look at what you’ve done!

582
00:33:09,904 --> 00:33:10,989
Look!

583
00:33:12,073 --> 00:33:13,282
God, Liv!

584
00:33:20,289 --> 00:33:21,749
I remember

585
00:33:23,334 --> 00:33:24,460
when

586
00:33:25,962 --> 00:33:28,089
you went into Zach’s office.

587
00:33:28,589 --> 00:33:32,927
You poured some eye
drops into his water bottle.

588
00:33:53,948 --> 00:33:54,907
[LIV SNIFFLES]

589
00:33:59,370 --> 00:34:00,580
[LIV SNIFFLES]

590
00:34:11,549 --> 00:34:12,508
[LIV SNIFFLES]

591
00:34:12,925 --> 00:34:14,135
[BOTTLE CAP CLANGS ON TABLE]

592
00:34:25,146 --> 00:34:26,689
[BOTTLE CAP CLICKS]

593
00:34:32,570 --> 00:34:33,446
[LIV SNIFFLES]

594
00:34:50,338 --> 00:34:54,050
I thought, “It’s just eye drops.

595
00:34:54,884 --> 00:34:59,680
What can eye drops do when ingested?”

596
00:35:00,765 --> 00:35:02,683
[SOBBING] It’s poison, Dad.

597
00:35:08,648 --> 00:35:13,444
I just realized it when the findings came out.

598
00:35:14,403 --> 00:35:17,115
That it was the cause of Zach’s death.

599
00:35:18,116 --> 00:35:19,951
I remembered what you did.

600
00:35:20,827 --> 00:35:25,248
[SOBBING] I-

601
00:35:25,623 --> 00:35:26,665
I can’t remember.

602
00:35:26,666 --> 00:35:28,459
I don’t remember anything.

603
00:35:29,377 --> 00:35:31,337
I don’t remember… [SOBS]

604
00:35:37,301 --> 00:35:38,886
I think

605
00:35:41,931 --> 00:35:43,850
it’s because I got traumatized.

606
00:35:44,517 --> 00:35:46,477
[SNIFFLES]

607
00:35:47,186 --> 00:35:48,812
I really don’t remember.

608
00:35:48,813 --> 00:35:51,232
I don’t remember anything.

609
00:35:54,735 --> 00:35:57,864
But Dad, why-

610
00:35:59,782 --> 00:36:02,451
[SOBBING] Why are you covering up for me?

611
00:36:02,827 --> 00:36:05,955
Why are you being punished
for what I did? [SOBS]

612
00:36:08,583 --> 00:36:09,917
Is that even a question?

613
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:12,086
A father...

614
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:14,755
- A parent—
- [LIV SNIFFLING]

615
00:36:16,465 --> 00:36:18,676
will do everything for their child.

616
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:20,178
Liv,

617
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:27,101
I will choose to be in jail on your behalf.

618
00:36:32,940 --> 00:36:34,442
You’re still young.

619
00:36:35,526 --> 00:36:37,445
I lived my life.

620
00:36:39,864 --> 00:36:41,115
Maybe

621
00:36:43,326 --> 00:36:44,911
this is my punishment for

622
00:36:45,703 --> 00:36:48,414
abandoning you and your mom.

623
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:52,835
Let this be my way of making up

624
00:36:53,044 --> 00:36:54,795
for all the times I failed you.

625
00:36:57,048 --> 00:36:58,758
I love you so much, Liv.

626
00:36:59,884 --> 00:37:03,763
Just promise me,

627
00:37:04,847 --> 00:37:07,683
the next time you fall in love,

628
00:37:10,686 --> 00:37:13,648
- you will get to know their real intentions.
- [LIV SOBBING]

629
00:37:15,399 --> 00:37:17,944
Make sure that they’re a good person.

630
00:37:30,915 --> 00:37:32,917
[LIV CRYING]

631
00:37:57,483 --> 00:38:00,778
I shouldn't be apologizing to you, Zach.

632
00:38:02,238 --> 00:38:04,073
What you did to me was

633
00:38:07,285 --> 00:38:09,078
unforgivable.

634
00:38:14,917 --> 00:38:16,919
But the truth is,

635
00:38:21,632 --> 00:38:24,969
I loved you.

636
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:32,351
But you were too damaged, to the
point that you damaged me, too.

637
00:38:36,605 --> 00:38:39,233
[SNIFFLES]

638
00:38:39,984 --> 00:38:41,193
[SIGHS]

639
00:38:53,873 --> 00:38:58,461
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

640
00:39:07,386 --> 00:39:09,597
[CHUCKLING]

641
00:39:13,559 --> 00:39:17,688
[INHALES DEEPLY]

642
00:39:20,274 --> 00:39:23,986
[BREATHES DEEPLY]

643
00:39:26,781 --> 00:39:28,240
[SIGHS]
